steps.name: Type Freestyle_Project_Name to name input field
Click on the Jenkins logo on the header
Click breadcrumbs arrow after project name to call menu
Type new name in input field on project rename page
Click 'Rename' button for confirmation when renamed via breadcrumbs
Click on the Jenkins logo on the header
Expected result: Renamed Freestyle Project is displayed on Home page
